message: Speedy Deletion, Steven G. Kaplan is not a primary creator of notable film content, his work is not notable and does not merit a Wikipedia page.
general notability in question. cleanup. not reliable facts.
/* Personal life */ no reference, material removed

Steven G. Kaplan is NOT a notable film producer. He is not worthy of a Wikipedia page, nor are his credits verifiable or of any commercial or artistic interest. Steven G. Kaplan, himself, has used Wikipedia to add FALSE information about himself.

There is absolutely no verification to what is being written, this article is completely not notable and is not worthy of a Wikipedia page. If one can write whatever they want about themselves on this, then what is the point? Ridiculous.
This article has been proposed for deletion as there are no references and this person has no credits of any note in the film industry.
